{"tid":661194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋輪候時間增至5.1年創新高","createTime":"2018-05-11T10:46:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T12:47:28.000Z","uid":59491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a95bbb013f1235c3dd082018461c0df1ace8015","tid":661194,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】房委會最新數字顯示，公屋一般申請者平均輪候時間增至5.1年，創十多年來新高。<br />\n<br />\n截至三月底，公屋一般申請者平均輪候時間5.1年，首度突破五年的大關，較去年底的4.7年大幅增加0.4年，當中長者一人申請者平均輪候時間為2.8年。<br />\n<br />\n截至三月，一共有15.3萬宗一般公屋申請，以及11.9萬宗在配額及計分制下的非長者一人申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=305455&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D305455%26refer%3D&d=u5qNS%2BofXBNJlJje3acABMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=1472b966\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D305455%26refer%3D&h=28c90efa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=305455&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"b390706fb1a76bc8b266959f4dcdb0aed47c864d","tid":661194,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"17f6aa89454a83c99d8055ac5f424cc0b2c6f4f8","tid":661194,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b390706fb1a76bc8b266959f4dcdb0aed47c864d","tid":661194,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822f92f819c72899a175cc21005d90f3898c773f","tid":661194,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"盡早改革公屋<br />\n市價折扣放租<br />\n起碼有得住"},{"pid":"5754a6463b18242f861629720f8be2f82a93e997","tid":661194,"uid":100276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime